{"tid":2123701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍戰機逼近中國領空 接被軍警告內容曝光","createTime":"2020-07-25T00:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T01:35:26.000Z","uid":48124,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7b2201c037cabd9c1b564a61fb28303774bb67","tid":2123701,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T00:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國軍機23日進入台灣西南方防空識別區，同時美軍也在台灣南部空域至東沙島附近巡視，台灣空軍則派出戰機驅離中國軍機。當天就有一位中國業餘無線電玩家錄到，美軍靠近中國領空時，共軍發出的無線電內容。<br />\n<br />\n北京大學「南海戰略態勢感知計畫」平台（SCS Probing Initiative）的推特23日發布，一位業餘無線電玩家錄到中國空軍警告內容，音檔前段是一名女性塔台人員與機長的對話，他們溝通到一半，突然間就傳出共軍的警示訊息。<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\nSCS平台推測，該段錄音應發生在7月23日台灣海峽以北的中國海岸一代，包括中文及英文警告，「我是中國海軍航空兵，你已接近我領空，立即離開，否則將遭到攔截，This is China Naval Air Force on guard.You are approaching Chinese air domain.Chang your course immediately,or you'll be intercepted.」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 美軍逼近中國領空！共機緊急起飛　警告無線電內容曝 | ETtoday軍武新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 手機版 | ETtoday MobileWeb <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200725/1768946.htm#ixzz6TACLd5eU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200725%2F1768946.htm%23ixzz6TACLd5eU&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=cfc2de0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200725/1768946.htm#ixzz6TACLd5eU</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"07d3fe32da7687039af98c43acfe94fbd6806cd3","tid":2123701,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T00:58:07.000Z","msg":"what are you sinking about d friend"},{"pid":"29ce27fe02452344532a6db2d5503dbac53e65e4","tid":2123701,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T00:58:55